The global motorcycle apparel market can be segmented based on product type, distribution channel, and price range. In terms of product type, the market offers a range of options including gloves, jackets, helmets, pants, boots, and others. Each of these products serves a specific purpose in providing protection and comfort to motorcycle riders. The distribution channels for motorcycle apparel include offline stores and online stores, allowing consumers to choose the most convenient way to make their purchases. Furthermore, the market can also be segmented based on price range, offering products in premium, mid, and low price categories to cater to a diverse range of consumers with varying budgets.

